Chua &amp; Aziz (2018), 
<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFEC8A0AF648EE14F59DC8B3" box="[2436,2584,4533,4560]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="314">Dejtaradol</emphasis>
(2009), Kingston 
<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFEC8A0AF4E4EE14F4C3C8B3" box="[2856,2886,4533,4560]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="314">et</emphasis>
al. (2006), Leong &amp; Lim (2009), 
<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFEC8A0AF2F5EE14F2EBC8B3" box="[3385,3438,4533,4560]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="314">Lim</emphasis>
et 
